Daytona System Test
===================

When the unit is switched on with one combination of the following key
presses, the appropiate test will start.

Right Shift + Page Up                      : Keyboard test
Right Shift + Page Down                    : Unit test; continous; full
Right Shift + Page Down + Page Up          : LCD test
Right Shift + Return                       : Unit test; single; full
Right Shift + Return + Page Up             : Unit test; single; part
Right Shift + Return + Page Down           : Unit test; continous; part
Right Shift + Return + Page Down + Page Up : BABT approval test
Right Shift + Delete                       : Buzzer test
Right Shift + Return + Delete              : LED Test
Right Shift + Delete + Page Down           : Buzzer and LED test
